data.description: Well cared for home in a fantastic, established neighborhood.  This is a great location right in the heart of West Ashley conveniently located minutes to grocery stores, shopping and restaurants.  The open floor plan connects the family room, dining area, and kitchen. Kitchen has an eat-in breakfast space, making it convenient for quick meals or casual dining. Fresh neutral paint, maple cabinets in kitchen, gas fireplace, large walk in closets and dual vanity/sinks in the master bath add to the enjoyment of this home. The back screened porch looks out over the large yard into the green way and woods in back of the house.
